              "description": "Automated onboarding flow for new car insurance policies using a virtual broker agent with Intelligent Document Processing.",
              "businessPriority": "High – value driver = productivity / target KPIs = minutes saved",
              "targetUsers": "Customers",
              "expectedOutcomes": "You can go through the entire quote, underwriting and issue policy flows for a new car policy entirely with an agent. This agent also must be able to ask for documents, and use it's content to pre-populate and validate information",
              "jobStories": [
                {
                  "story": "When a customer is interested in a new car insurance, he needs to go through the flow to get a quote. It should be able to generate a quote entirely conversation driven.",
                  "painPoints": "Make sure all questions are asked in a natural way\nWork in multiple systems\nIntegration between Core platform (Keylane Axon), Salesforce",
                  "desiredOutcomes": "95% accuracy in responses",
                  "kpis": "Time savedAverage handling time"
                },
                {
                  "story": "When a customer has accepted a new car policy offer, I want Agentforce to gather all required documents and data, validate it and if acceptable issue the new policy. If there is any doubt there should be a hand off to a customer agent.",
                  "painPoints": "\nWork in multiple systems\nMultiple email between customer and service agent",
                  "desiredOutcomes": "95% accuracy in responses",
                  "kpis": "Time savedAverage handling time"
                },
                {
                  "story": "All the required documents (such as proof for damage free years) should be asked and interpreted automatically and update on axon and/or salesforce to make sure that no unnecessary mails are send",
                  "painPoints": "Over communication to the customer\nmanual validation is low priority but risk",
                  "desiredOutcomes": "Automatically approve received documents",
                  "kpis": "less time spend by back-office teams"
                }
              ],
              "scope": {
                "agentRole": "AI agent (Agentforce) deployed in Salesforce to automate handling of gathering all required documents and data for completion of a new car policy request",
                "channels": "Chat",
                "currentProcess": "Manual: after an offer has been accepted, multiple mails between customer and service agent to gather documents and data",
                "functionalScopeIn": "New car policy request",
                "functionalScopeOut": "Any other car policy mutation request",
                "data": "- Case record\n- Contract records in Salesforce\n- Documents in Axon\n- Conversation history",
                "actions": "- Request document\n- Check document correct\n- Check document complete\n- Consolidate cases\n- Hand off service agent\n- Escalate",
                "guardrails": "- Never provide advise\n- Don't use subjective adjectives\n- Don't compare to other insurers\n- If about claims, route to claims department",
